WEBVTT

01:27.440 --> 01:31.880
[The Dark Romance]

01:32.170 --> 01:34.920
[Episode 18]

01:45.710 --> 01:47.170
What are you doing, Honey?

01:49.430 --> 01:50.430
Beef pancakes?

01:50.650 --> 01:52.580
Yes, I looked up the recipe online.

01:52.640 --> 01:54.710
Jiale loves the pancakes
Leilei made the most.

01:54.710 --> 01:55.410
I know.

01:59.310 --> 02:00.020
Honey,

02:00.430 --> 02:01.890
thanks for your hard work.

02:03.090 --> 02:04.090
It's my pleasure.

02:05.350 --> 02:06.680
There's so much smoke.

02:07.920 --> 02:08.720
You're awake?

02:10.030 --> 02:11.450
What's this smell? It smells great!

02:11.450 --> 02:13.150
Didn't you say you were craving this?

02:13.150 --> 02:14.810
Your favorite beef pancakes.

02:16.060 --> 02:18.860
But it's quite difficult
to make it for the first time.

02:18.860 --> 02:20.720
It looks like the house is on fire.

02:21.030 --> 02:21.560
Honey,

02:21.650 --> 02:22.750
the smoke is too thick.

02:22.750 --> 02:23.750
Please help open the windows

02:23.750 --> 02:25.610
-and the door to air it out.
-Okay.

02:25.680 --> 02:27.610
The range hood doesn't help at all.

02:29.360 --> 02:29.870
Jiale.

02:30.310 --> 02:30.770
Come on,

02:31.870 --> 02:32.730
help me taste it

02:32.870 --> 02:34.670
and see if it's the right flavor.

02:38.280 --> 02:39.079
Not bad.

02:39.280 --> 02:40.010
Not bad, huh?

02:40.150 --> 02:40.840
But

02:41.600 --> 02:42.280
the ones Godmother made

02:42.280 --> 02:45.079
seemed to have a slightly pungent taste.

02:46.470 --> 02:47.400
A pungent taste?

02:48.310 --> 02:50.110
Could it be Sichuan peppercorn?

02:50.120 --> 02:50.620
Yeah.

02:50.870 --> 02:51.910
The taste of Sichuan peppercorn.

02:51.910 --> 02:52.960
Then f-forget about this one.

02:52.960 --> 02:53.890
I'll improve it.

02:54.750 --> 02:55.550
Just a moment.

02:56.520 --> 02:58.050
Look at how serious you are.

02:59.120 --> 03:00.680
You're almost
like a scientific researcher.

03:00.680 --> 03:01.940
Of course I'm serious.

03:02.310 --> 03:03.750
Jiale is my buddy now.

03:03.750 --> 03:04.800
I must help my buddy

03:04.800 --> 03:05.750
fulfill his wish.

03:05.750 --> 03:06.160
Right?

03:06.240 --> 03:07.170
Thanks, big bro.

03:07.310 --> 03:08.310
Don't mention it.

03:08.520 --> 03:10.240
Seems like I can only be an assistant

03:10.240 --> 03:11.640
and dispose of the trash.

03:12.960 --> 03:13.510
Honey,

03:13.750 --> 03:15.520
there's some chicken left from last night.

03:15.520 --> 03:17.360
Aren't there
quite a few stray cats downstairs?

03:17.360 --> 03:19.030
Do you want to take Jiale
to feed them together?

03:19.030 --> 03:20.079
I want to go.

03:20.079 --> 03:21.470
Jiale, give me some time.

03:21.470 --> 03:22.240
I'll wrap it up real quick.

03:22.240 --> 03:24.040
It will be ready when you come up.

03:25.310 --> 03:26.770
Jiale, change your shoes.

03:26.870 --> 03:27.560
It's raining outside.

03:27.560 --> 03:28.760
I'll get an umbrella.

03:35.310 --> 03:36.950
Honey, we'll be right back.

03:37.120 --> 03:37.590
Okay.

03:37.590 --> 03:38.750
I'll leave the door open.

03:38.750 --> 03:39.240
Okay.

03:45.630 --> 03:47.329
Where are the kitties?

03:47.800 --> 03:49.150
It's pouring rain today.

03:49.150 --> 03:51.480
Are the cats all hiding
and not coming out?

03:57.870 --> 03:59.130
Where are the kitties?

04:00.600 --> 04:01.060
Come on.

04:01.630 --> 04:03.160
Help Mom open the trash can.

04:04.710 --> 04:05.310
Thank you.

04:07.870 --> 04:09.310
They seem to be over there.

04:09.310 --> 04:09.750
Look.

04:10.150 --> 04:11.280
Let's go take a look.

04:12.360 --> 04:13.680
I even heard a cat meowing.

04:13.680 --> 04:14.310
Really?

04:17.950 --> 04:19.149
They really are here.

04:19.240 --> 04:19.690
Look.

04:19.720 --> 04:20.829
What are they eating?

04:20.829 --> 04:22.630
They already have something to eat.

04:22.630 --> 04:23.760
Has anyone fed them?

04:34.170 --> 04:34.680
Mom,

04:34.680 --> 04:35.540
what is that?

04:36.190 --> 04:37.000
What is it?

04:40.390 --> 04:41.450
Don't look, Jiale.

04:41.870 --> 04:43.070
I-Is it Cola?

04:43.070 --> 04:44.240
Don't look, don't look.

04:44.240 --> 04:44.510
Don't.

04:44.510 --> 04:45.070
Cola!

04:45.070 --> 04:45.730
Don't look.

04:46.270 --> 04:47.310
It's Cola!

04:55.480 --> 04:57.100
I really closed the cage.

04:57.310 --> 04:58.720
I remember it clearly.

04:59.510 --> 05:01.010
Did you forget to lock it?

05:01.480 --> 05:04.480
You have to twist it to the right
after closing the door.

05:04.480 --> 05:06.230
I did twist it. I did.

05:06.480 --> 05:08.270
I remember I did this.

05:10.510 --> 05:11.920
But after dinner yesterday,

05:11.920 --> 05:12.630
Jiale and I

05:12.630 --> 05:14.040
never fed Cola again.

05:14.390 --> 05:17.390
It couldn't have opened the cage
and run out by itself.

05:27.870 --> 05:28.690
Jiale,

05:29.120 --> 05:29.860
stop crying.

05:30.800 --> 05:31.860
Mom will go with you

05:32.270 --> 05:33.570
to bury Cola.

05:34.070 --> 05:35.390
We'll get a new one.

05:35.600 --> 05:36.330
Is that good?

05:36.480 --> 05:37.570
No!

05:37.630 --> 05:39.290
It's not the same at all!

05:39.510 --> 05:42.159
Cola is dead and will never come back!

05:42.240 --> 05:44.390
It was you who killed Cola.

05:44.390 --> 05:46.110
Why don't you admit it?

05:46.680 --> 05:48.070
It really wasn't me.

05:48.120 --> 05:49.480
You are always like this.

05:49.480 --> 05:51.630
You got Grandpa killed back then

05:51.630 --> 05:53.800
and left Grandma alone
for the rest of her life.

05:53.800 --> 05:55.409
You're so selfish!

05:55.800 --> 05:57.430
You made mistakes
and didn't dare to admit them.

05:57.430 --> 05:59.290
Instead, you only blamed others.

06:00.120 --> 06:00.720
Jiale.

06:05.310 --> 06:06.000
Jiale.

06:08.510 --> 06:09.870
Jiale, open the door

06:09.870 --> 06:11.330
and let Mom explain, okay?

06:11.720 --> 06:12.630
I don't want to hear it!

06:12.630 --> 06:14.560
I only want Cola back!

06:15.070 --> 06:16.800
Open the door first, okay?

06:16.800 --> 06:18.390
Let Mom explain, please.

06:19.600 --> 06:20.240
Jiale.

06:22.120 --> 06:22.600
Jia...

06:24.610 --> 06:25.750
Give him some time.

06:26.310 --> 06:28.240
You also heard what he just said.

06:29.270 --> 06:31.130
How could he think of me like that?

06:31.690 --> 06:33.620
He's just overwhelmed with grief.

06:34.040 --> 06:35.310
Facing Cola's death,

06:35.480 --> 06:36.880
finding someone to blame

06:36.920 --> 06:38.780
can make him feel a little better.

06:39.120 --> 06:41.520
This is a common way people
deal with grief.

06:42.240 --> 06:44.070
When Leilei and your mom passed away,

06:44.070 --> 06:45.330
didn't you do the same?

06:48.070 --> 06:48.850
Yesterday,

06:49.450 --> 06:50.710
after feeding Cola,

06:52.280 --> 06:54.140
I really did close the cage.

06:55.510 --> 06:56.920
I really twisted it.

06:58.000 --> 06:59.480
I remember it clearly.

07:00.800 --> 07:01.600
I admit,

07:02.480 --> 07:04.540
when I opened the window and the door,

07:04.630 --> 07:05.800
I didn't notice

07:05.800 --> 07:07.600
if Cola was still in the cage.

07:08.800 --> 07:11.460
If only I hadn't opened
the windows and the door.

07:13.000 --> 07:14.330
What do you mean by that?

07:17.270 --> 07:18.680
So you're blaming me now?

07:19.270 --> 07:20.680
It's because I told you to open the door

07:20.680 --> 07:21.870
that Cola ran away?

07:23.950 --> 07:25.270
I didn't mean that.

07:25.920 --> 07:27.520
But the way you put it just now

07:28.190 --> 07:29.390
will make Jiale think

07:29.720 --> 07:31.190
it's all my fault.

07:31.830 --> 07:33.210
So Jiale was right.

07:34.070 --> 07:36.270
You just need someone to take the blame,

07:36.600 --> 07:37.600
someone to blame.

07:38.070 --> 07:39.720
So that person is me now.

07:39.890 --> 07:41.040
I didn't say that.

07:42.040 --> 07:42.720
I just feel...

07:42.720 --> 07:43.830
"I," "I," "I."

07:44.240 --> 07:46.170
"I feel," "I think," "I remember."

07:46.270 --> 07:48.130
Why do you only think of yourself?

07:48.159 --> 07:49.390
Other people's efforts and feelings

07:49.390 --> 07:50.520
mean nothing to you.

07:55.070 --> 07:56.800
Don't twist my words.

08:02.000 --> 08:03.530
Let's talk inside the room.

08:12.720 --> 08:13.560
I'll be blunt.

08:14.720 --> 08:16.580
You say you want to comfort Jiale,

08:17.390 --> 08:20.120
but have you ever
really cared about his feelings?

08:20.120 --> 08:20.950
He's only 10.

08:21.920 --> 08:23.630
Do you even know how much pressure

08:23.630 --> 08:25.120
and grievance he has endured

08:25.120 --> 08:26.320
because of your mess?

08:26.510 --> 08:27.840
When he chatted with me,

08:28.240 --> 08:30.920
he told me that his classmates were
all gossiping about you,

08:30.920 --> 08:32.250
which made him so upset,

08:32.390 --> 08:34.190
but he didn't know how to refute.

08:34.510 --> 08:37.110
He has endured
all of this silently by himself.

08:39.120 --> 08:39.960
I admit

08:41.440 --> 08:42.440
that my situation

08:43.000 --> 08:44.730
would make Jiale very confused

08:45.200 --> 08:45.990
and upset.

08:46.630 --> 08:48.360
Because it's too complicated.

08:49.030 --> 08:51.430
I don't know
how to explain it to him either.

08:51.630 --> 08:53.360
But that's a different matter.

08:54.120 --> 08:55.720
I really locked the cage.

08:55.740 --> 08:57.340
You can't accuse me wrongly.

08:58.240 --> 08:59.320
Yeah, yeah.

09:00.390 --> 09:02.120
You are always a victim,

09:02.630 --> 09:04.320
always the one getting hurt.

09:05.080 --> 09:06.280
Your father's death,

09:06.910 --> 09:08.720
your mother's lifelong pain,

09:09.440 --> 09:10.790
your one-night stand with Lu,

09:10.790 --> 09:11.910
and Jiale's birth.

09:12.200 --> 09:13.010
Tell me.

09:13.240 --> 09:16.170
Do you really have no responsibility
for all of this?

09:16.200 --> 09:17.000
You don't dare to accept

09:17.000 --> 09:19.670
the fact that your life was
messed up by yourself.

09:19.670 --> 09:21.390
So you must always be right,

09:21.480 --> 09:22.270
righteous,

09:22.790 --> 09:23.720
and fair.

09:24.380 --> 09:26.670
It's always other people
who cause mistakes.

09:26.670 --> 09:27.720
To prove this,

09:28.080 --> 09:29.670
you even tried to put the blame

09:29.670 --> 09:30.670
on me just now

09:31.320 --> 09:33.050
in order to ease your own guilt.

09:36.080 --> 09:36.630
No.

09:38.000 --> 09:39.130
That's not true.

09:39.750 --> 09:40.160
I...

09:40.630 --> 09:41.200
No.

09:41.200 --> 09:42.200
At this moment,

09:42.710 --> 09:44.240
when Jiale is in deep grief,

09:44.600 --> 09:46.790
shouldn't you, his mother,

09:46.790 --> 09:48.610
do whatever it takes

09:48.840 --> 09:50.870
to make him feel a bit better?

09:51.720 --> 09:52.750
But what you care about is still

09:52.750 --> 09:54.610
whether you are wrongly accused.

10:21.910 --> 10:22.390
Hello?

10:23.440 --> 10:24.040
What's up?

10:25.080 --> 10:25.940
Is this Xiao Su?

10:26.480 --> 10:28.790
I'm a police officer
from Dongqiao Police Station in Wuzhou.

10:28.790 --> 10:30.990
Your mother, Hua Sanmei, is with us now.

10:35.600 --> 10:36.200
Hello.

10:37.910 --> 10:39.240
What happened to my mom?

10:39.720 --> 10:42.150
You know the girl
who lives with your mother,

10:42.150 --> 10:42.750
right?

10:45.480 --> 10:46.810
She is a patient of mine.

10:47.500 --> 10:48.710
I am a psychiatrist.

10:49.840 --> 10:51.900
This patient has no other relatives,

10:52.440 --> 10:55.110
and her stepfather is unwilling
to take care of her.

10:55.110 --> 10:57.560
Besides, her condition
took a turn for the worse a while ago.

10:57.560 --> 10:58.630
The nursing hospital raised its prices,

10:58.630 --> 11:00.000
and she couldn't afford them.

11:00.000 --> 11:01.560
So I took her to my hometown

11:02.080 --> 11:03.740
and let my mom take care of her.

11:04.320 --> 11:05.870
But your mother insists

11:05.870 --> 11:07.000
that this girl is

11:07.360 --> 11:08.750
your sister, Xiao Yuan.

11:12.960 --> 11:13.590
My sister

11:14.600 --> 11:16.400
didn't get along with our family

11:18.150 --> 11:20.210
and ran away from home many years ago.

11:20.580 --> 11:22.780
There has been no news of her ever since.

11:22.910 --> 11:24.440
It was a huge blow to my mom.

11:25.450 --> 11:26.780
Maybe deep down inside,

11:27.670 --> 11:29.870
she really hopes that girl is my sister.

11:30.390 --> 11:31.770
I think this is good, too.

11:31.770 --> 11:34.300
If she takes care of her
like her own daughter,

11:34.840 --> 11:36.570
it's also good for the patient.

11:37.000 --> 11:39.670
Did you prescribe the medicine
for this girl?

11:40.680 --> 11:41.880
Yes, I prescribed it.

11:43.910 --> 11:45.570
Which hospital do you work at?

11:45.710 --> 11:48.390
I work in the Psychiatry Department
at Lihai Renxin Hospital

11:48.390 --> 11:49.050
as a doctor.

11:50.270 --> 11:50.800
Officer,

11:51.680 --> 11:53.280
I want to explain something.

11:53.910 --> 11:56.340
When I retook the college entrance exam,
for my student status,

11:56.340 --> 11:58.000
I changed my name to Luo Liang.

11:58.620 --> 11:59.920
My dad got this done.

12:00.390 --> 12:01.990
My mom doesn't know about it.

12:04.870 --> 12:05.440
Officer,

12:06.930 --> 12:08.280
what on earth happened?

12:09.380 --> 12:11.580
Your mother gave her
3 times the dosage.

12:12.360 --> 12:13.640
That was a lethal dose.

12:16.910 --> 12:17.790
My mom is undereducated

12:17.790 --> 12:19.270
and can't read the medicine names.

12:19.270 --> 12:22.000
I taught her how to give them
based on colors and sizes.

12:22.000 --> 12:24.120
Which medicine did she wrongly give Shan?

12:24.120 --> 12:25.650
How is Shan doing right now?

12:26.550 --> 12:29.240
Luckily, your mother
called an ambulance in time.

12:29.240 --> 12:30.840
So the girl barely survived.

12:37.080 --> 12:38.080
That's great.

12:39.530 --> 12:40.730
Thank God she's fine.

12:50.320 --> 12:51.080
How did your mother

12:51.080 --> 12:52.320
get this medicine?

12:53.910 --> 12:54.910
Here's the thing.

12:59.600 --> 13:01.060
It's prescription drugs,

13:01.630 --> 13:03.090
which can't be couriered.

13:03.490 --> 13:05.150
So I sent them by regular mail.

13:06.030 --> 13:07.880
What's this girl's real name?

13:08.320 --> 13:10.580
Which sanatorium did you take her out of?

13:11.670 --> 13:13.000
Her name is Qiao Zishan.

13:15.280 --> 13:16.740
She's from Harbor Island.

13:18.450 --> 13:21.580
She used to live
in Minkang Sanatorium on Harbor Island.

13:25.240 --> 13:25.970
Dr. Luo is

13:26.000 --> 13:27.060
a volunteer doctor

13:27.150 --> 13:28.810
at our sanatorium,

13:29.170 --> 13:31.570
who has taken care
of Zishan for many years.

13:31.570 --> 13:33.480
Zishan's mother died in the fire
set by herself,

13:33.480 --> 13:35.360
and it was Dr. Luo
who rushed into the fire

13:35.360 --> 13:36.360
and saved Zishan.

13:36.630 --> 13:39.230
She originally planned to study
art and design

13:39.600 --> 13:41.630
after graduating from City University.

13:41.630 --> 13:43.740
But her mother suddenly went crazy

13:43.820 --> 13:44.750
and set the fire,

13:45.120 --> 13:46.050
destroying her.

13:46.120 --> 13:46.870
What a pity.

13:48.910 --> 13:52.120
Were it not for Dr. Luo,
who's been covering her medical bills,

13:52.120 --> 13:53.630
she probably would have died long ago,

13:53.630 --> 13:55.160
relying on his stepfather.

13:55.510 --> 13:56.240
Then why did Dr. Luo

13:56.240 --> 13:58.030
take Qiao Zishan out of the sanatorium?

13:58.030 --> 13:59.700
Our place was acquired recently,

13:59.700 --> 14:00.840
and all prices went up.

14:00.840 --> 14:01.750
No way her stepfather

14:00.990 --> 14:02.880
[Automatic doors. Do not loiter.]

14:01.750 --> 14:02.850
could afford them.

14:02.940 --> 14:04.650
Besides, having an old man

14:05.080 --> 14:06.110
take care of a girl

14:06.390 --> 14:08.320
who is not related to him by blood is

14:08.630 --> 14:09.960
not appropriate at all!

14:10.670 --> 14:11.670
I'm a doctor.

14:14.090 --> 14:15.900
I treat every patient equally.

14:16.410 --> 14:19.270
How could he have
any ulterior motives towards her?

14:19.670 --> 14:20.670
Dr. Luo

14:20.670 --> 14:22.330
treats patients all the same.

14:22.390 --> 14:24.630
I think he just has
a benevolent heart as a doctor.

14:24.630 --> 14:27.210
He's especially supportive of the weak

14:27.270 --> 14:28.480
and vulnerable.

14:28.480 --> 14:30.000
So, the staff in our place,

14:30.000 --> 14:31.000
including me,

14:31.070 --> 14:32.530
all respect him very much.

14:33.090 --> 14:34.750
If there's anything special,

14:36.670 --> 14:37.510
it might be because

14:37.510 --> 14:39.270
I saved her life in the fire.

14:41.960 --> 14:44.160
I want her to live well more than anyone.

14:50.750 --> 14:51.550
Wait a moment.

15:00.930 --> 15:01.480
[The First Affiliated Hospital
of Wuzhou Medical University]

15:01.480 --> 15:02.180
[Physical Checkup Form]

15:02.200 --> 15:03.640
[Surgery] [Internal Medicine]
[Blood Routine]

15:07.730 --> 15:08.370
Xiao Su.

15:09.750 --> 15:11.100
We just verified it.

15:11.670 --> 15:13.540
What you said is basically true.

15:13.870 --> 15:14.980
From what we know,

15:15.080 --> 15:16.750
your mother has also been taking

15:16.750 --> 15:18.150
good care of Qiao Zishan.

15:18.360 --> 15:20.760
This incident might indeed be a slip-up,

15:21.480 --> 15:23.680
and we'll close the case as an accident.

15:23.790 --> 15:26.130
But you must remind your mother

15:26.360 --> 15:28.560
of never making the same mistake again.

15:30.170 --> 15:31.220
That's for sure.

15:33.000 --> 15:33.670
I will.

15:51.830 --> 15:52.810
[Calls]

15:53.110 --> 15:57.520
[July 15, 2019, Monday]

16:11.370 --> 16:13.490
[July 15, 2019, Monday]

16:35.890 --> 16:39.010
[July 15, 2019, Monday]

16:48.630 --> 16:49.430
Jiale.

16:49.840 --> 16:50.960
Where are you going?

16:50.960 --> 16:51.960
To my dad's place.

16:52.000 --> 16:54.460
I've already talked to him
and Ms. Fang Fang.

16:54.870 --> 16:55.910
Let Mom give you a lift then.

16:55.910 --> 16:56.440
No need!

16:56.440 --> 16:57.910
I don't need you to give me a lift.

16:57.910 --> 16:59.370
I'll have my dad pick me up.

16:59.510 --> 17:00.120
Jiale.

17:00.870 --> 17:02.070
I'll go down with you.

17:02.320 --> 17:03.580
It's raining outside.

17:33.110 --> 17:33.640
Hello.

17:33.640 --> 17:34.310
Hello, hello.

17:34.310 --> 17:35.200
Here's his luggage.

17:35.200 --> 17:35.530
Okay.

17:36.030 --> 17:37.390
Please take care of him
for a couple of days.

17:37.390 --> 17:38.440
Of course. As I should.

17:38.440 --> 17:39.570
All right, let's go.

17:40.110 --> 17:40.510
Jiale.

17:45.070 --> 17:46.100
Don't be sad.

17:46.480 --> 17:47.730
Stop crying.

17:52.390 --> 17:53.920
When Jiale is in deep grief,

17:54.920 --> 17:57.120
shouldn't you, his mother,

17:57.590 --> 17:59.530
do whatever it takes

17:59.640 --> 18:01.400
to make him feel a bit better?

18:33.070 --> 18:33.910
Thank you

18:33.960 --> 18:35.620
for dropping Jiale off for me.

18:38.440 --> 18:39.570
I am his father, too.

18:41.240 --> 18:41.920
I'm sorry.

18:45.030 --> 18:45.920
You are right.

18:48.480 --> 18:50.480
I really am not a good mother.

19:05.960 --> 19:07.820
No matter what mistakes you make,

19:09.440 --> 19:10.970
we will always forgive you.

19:12.240 --> 19:13.480
We are family.

19:20.290 --> 19:21.070
It's fine.

19:23.070 --> 19:23.980
Let him stay there for a few days.

19:23.980 --> 19:24.780
It'll be okay.

19:28.920 --> 19:29.520
Don't cry.

19:52.310 --> 19:53.570
Let me take a break, take a break.

19:53.570 --> 19:54.020
I can't

19:54.110 --> 19:55.510
do this anymore, Paw Patrol.

19:55.510 --> 19:57.570
I surrender. I'm out. I can't do this.

20:01.680 --> 20:02.940
Tell me about the case.

20:08.750 --> 20:09.640
He Xiao's son

20:10.750 --> 20:11.640
personally confirmed

20:11.640 --> 20:13.680
that his private tutor
at that time was called Luo Liang.

20:13.680 --> 20:14.280
Moreover,

20:14.680 --> 20:16.680
He Xiao also financially supported

20:16.830 --> 20:18.830
Luo Liang's studies on Harbor Island.

20:18.830 --> 20:21.560
That can only prove
that they were lovers at most.

20:21.770 --> 20:23.410
It doesn't mean he is Mister.

20:24.230 --> 20:25.790
Nor does it prove
that he has anything to do

20:25.790 --> 20:26.990
with He Xiao's death.

20:27.550 --> 20:28.160
I know.

20:29.350 --> 20:30.950
So I went straight to see him.

20:31.710 --> 20:33.770
I even booked an expert appointment.

20:34.000 --> 20:35.000
Sit down, please.

20:36.160 --> 20:37.090
Just put it here.

20:39.400 --> 20:40.800
Is there anything wrong?

20:40.960 --> 20:42.360
He's completely normal.

20:42.920 --> 20:44.790
I can't see any flaws at all.

20:45.920 --> 20:47.520
So I don't know what to do now.

20:48.030 --> 20:50.070
Do you think I should talk to Ms. Yan

20:52.070 --> 20:53.450
and tell her

20:53.630 --> 20:54.600
all we know?

20:58.480 --> 21:00.010
What are you worried about?

21:01.510 --> 21:03.120
They just got married.

21:03.830 --> 21:05.210
From what Ms. Yan said,

21:05.650 --> 21:07.450
they're pretty happy together.

21:08.480 --> 21:09.680
We are just guessing now.

21:09.680 --> 21:11.030
What if he is not Mister?

21:11.330 --> 21:12.680
If I go to Ms. Yan

21:12.680 --> 21:13.240
and say,

21:14.400 --> 21:15.270
"Your husband is

21:15.270 --> 21:17.280
the boss of Xia Yi and the others.

21:17.480 --> 21:18.750
About that PUA stuff,

21:18.750 --> 21:20.440
they've learned it all from your husband."

21:20.440 --> 21:21.970
Ms. Yan would lose her mind!

21:23.960 --> 21:25.380
Chief Hu said before

21:26.640 --> 21:28.040
that when we solve cases,

21:28.480 --> 21:30.080
we must presume innocence.

21:30.960 --> 21:32.420
While pursuing the truth,

21:32.960 --> 21:35.310
we must also seek kindness and compassion.

21:35.310 --> 21:35.880
Right?

21:56.350 --> 21:59.720
[Luo Liang] [Xiao Su] [Wuzhou]

21:57.110 --> 21:57.960
You made this?

21:59.630 --> 22:02.440
No kidding. I didn't stay
in the Special Crimes Unit for nothing.

22:02.440 --> 22:03.120
Look.

22:04.350 --> 22:05.000
Luo Liang.

22:05.680 --> 22:06.370
No.

22:06.790 --> 22:08.350
He wasn't called Luo Liang back then.

22:08.350 --> 22:09.030
Xiao Su

22:08.600 --> 22:13.040
[Dongguang, First Love, Xu Jingyun]

22:10.040 --> 22:12.270
got admitted to Nanshan Medical University

22:12.270 --> 22:13.470
in Dongguang in 1999.

22:15.770 --> 22:16.490
In 2000,

22:17.070 --> 22:20.200
he was sentenced to 3 years in prison
for attempted rape.

22:20.350 --> 22:22.030
One year after his release from prison,

22:22.030 --> 22:23.110
in 2004,

22:24.480 --> 22:26.240
he changed his face and identity

22:26.240 --> 22:27.280
and got admitted

22:27.310 --> 22:30.070
to Tianfu Medical University
in Chengyu City again.

22:27.410 --> 22:28.990
[Chengyu, Private Tutor, He Xiao]

22:30.070 --> 22:31.150
He Xiao's home was

22:31.590 --> 22:32.920
in Chengyu at that time.

22:33.680 --> 22:34.980
In 2007,

22:35.350 --> 22:38.410
Luo Liang was hired
as a private tutor in He Xiao's home.

22:39.350 --> 22:42.270
My mom often invited him
to stay for dinner.

22:43.410 --> 22:45.730
We were like a family.

22:48.590 --> 22:49.920
In 2009,

22:50.070 --> 22:50.920
Xie Ke

22:51.890 --> 22:52.680
went to Chengyu

22:52.090 --> 22:56.010
[Bingyuan, Volunteer, Xie Ke]

22:52.680 --> 22:53.830
to participate

22:53.850 --> 22:57.000
in the skating competition
of the Oya Youth Games that year.

22:57.000 --> 22:57.930
I've checked it.

22:58.270 --> 22:59.530
In the Games that year,

22:59.830 --> 23:01.680
countless students
from Tianfu Medical University

23:01.680 --> 23:03.610
served as volunteers in the arena.

23:05.690 --> 23:07.290
Sir, please have some water.

23:13.680 --> 23:14.480
Here is water.

23:29.030 --> 23:32.880
[Oya Youth Games
Figure Skating Championships]

23:32.940 --> 23:34.270
[For Media]

23:41.990 --> 23:43.290
For Xie Ke,

23:44.200 --> 23:46.110
he ruthlessly dumped He Xiao,

23:46.110 --> 23:47.910
even though He Xiao was pregnant

23:48.200 --> 23:49.510
with Luo Liang's child at that time.

23:49.510 --> 23:50.160
Exactly.

23:50.550 --> 23:51.750
Early in 2010,

23:51.880 --> 23:53.310
He Xiao was unwilling to let go.

23:53.310 --> 23:54.510
To win back her lover,

23:54.570 --> 23:57.470
she went to Bingyuan City to find Xie Ke

23:57.680 --> 23:59.940
and begged her to break up with Luo Liang.

24:00.200 --> 24:01.330
I'd give up my family

24:01.790 --> 24:03.340
as well as my child.

24:03.510 --> 24:04.970
All I want is him.

24:05.270 --> 24:06.830
But the begging didn't work.

24:06.830 --> 24:08.880
He Xiao committed suicide in Bingyuan,

24:08.880 --> 24:11.610
showing Xie Ke her despair through death,

24:11.960 --> 24:13.640
and demonstrating her love for Luo Liang.

24:13.640 --> 24:14.310
Exactly.

24:14.930 --> 24:17.150
Not long after He Xiao's suicide,

24:17.170 --> 24:18.430
before a competition,

24:18.750 --> 24:20.960
Xie Ke suddenly learned about this

24:20.960 --> 24:22.160
from a companion of hers.

24:22.160 --> 24:22.750
But I do know

24:22.750 --> 24:24.640
even the greatest love
can't be built on someone's death,

24:24.640 --> 24:26.030
for there will be retribution!

24:26.030 --> 24:27.490
She was all over the place.

24:27.750 --> 24:29.070
That was why she made a mistake

24:29.070 --> 24:30.680
when performing that difficult move.

24:30.680 --> 24:31.550
Then her partner

24:31.550 --> 24:34.420
touched the wound from her recent tattoo,

24:35.790 --> 24:37.270
causing Xie Ke to accidentally fall

24:37.270 --> 24:38.550
in that competition.

24:44.750 --> 24:46.200
In 2010,

24:46.450 --> 24:48.790
Luo Liang had already used
the money given by He Xiao

24:48.790 --> 24:51.350
to get into the Medical School
of Xiangjiang University on Harbor Island

24:51.350 --> 24:52.160
for his PhD.

24:54.830 --> 24:56.090
Just a few years later,

24:56.460 --> 24:57.950
[Shenchuan, Wei Zhihua]

24:56.550 --> 24:57.830
Wei Zhihua, a hairdresser

24:57.830 --> 25:00.230
working in Shenchuan, committed suicide.

25:00.510 --> 25:01.240
Yes,

25:00.530 --> 25:03.220
[Chloe]

25:01.240 --> 25:02.470
Zhihua.

25:02.880 --> 25:04.610
She was so pretty.

25:05.030 --> 25:06.090
Don't you get it?

25:06.640 --> 25:07.440
I guess

25:07.440 --> 25:10.900
it's highly likely
that during Luo Liang's doctoral studies,

25:11.000 --> 25:13.970
while traveling
between Harbor Island and Shenchuan,

25:13.970 --> 25:15.410
he met this hairdresser.

25:22.510 --> 25:25.240
Because he made an acquaintance
with the hairdresser, Wei Zhihua,

25:25.240 --> 25:27.890
Luo Liang dumped Xie Ke.

25:34.160 --> 25:35.890
Where have you been for so long?

25:41.590 --> 25:43.650
I've been studying on Harbor Island.

25:44.410 --> 25:46.540
Then why didn't you come back to see me?

25:48.960 --> 25:49.720
As you know,

25:50.240 --> 25:52.100
I'm very busy with my coursework.

25:55.270 --> 25:57.830
Did you fall in love
with someone else again?

25:59.850 --> 26:01.310
What kind of person is she?

26:09.590 --> 26:11.030
She is a very simple girl,

26:13.880 --> 26:14.590
unlike you,

26:15.330 --> 26:17.390
who are so aloof and hard to approach.

26:17.860 --> 26:19.430
I am not like that.

26:21.400 --> 26:22.460
She loves me so much

26:23.290 --> 26:24.960
that when I said I wanted a child,

26:24.960 --> 26:25.880
she agreed immediately.

26:25.880 --> 26:27.200
I love you, too.

26:27.200 --> 26:28.510
I can do the same.

26:31.210 --> 26:32.610
I don't want to lie to you.

26:34.070 --> 26:35.870
So don't lie to yourself either.

26:38.390 --> 26:39.390
Look at yourself.

26:43.410 --> 26:44.870
Look at the way you are now.

26:48.660 --> 26:50.460
How are we supposed to continue?

26:51.930 --> 26:52.880
No.

26:52.880 --> 26:54.480
Please don't leave me.

26:54.510 --> 26:55.770
-Let me go.
-I'm now...

26:56.310 --> 26:57.170
Don't go.

26:57.720 --> 26:58.480
No.

27:00.440 --> 27:01.520
L-Look.

27:01.550 --> 27:02.640
Look, I can.

27:02.640 --> 27:04.030
I'm recovering now.

27:04.200 --> 27:05.110
I'm begging you.

27:05.110 --> 27:06.880
Please give me another chance, okay?

27:06.880 --> 27:08.710
Don't leave me.

27:08.880 --> 27:10.350
Come on. Look at yourself.

27:10.710 --> 27:12.510
Look at the way you are right now.

27:17.310 --> 27:18.970
Do you still look like a woman?

28:15.030 --> 28:16.590
In the autumn of 2011,

28:17.070 --> 28:20.310
Xie Ke traveled all the way
from Bingyuan to Chengyu,

28:20.310 --> 28:22.270
and at the stadium
where she once competed in the Games,

28:22.270 --> 28:23.590
she leaped to her death.

28:23.590 --> 28:24.480
People all thought

28:24.480 --> 28:27.590
she was commemorating the place
where she once won the championship.

28:27.590 --> 28:28.480
But in fact,

28:29.240 --> 28:32.400
that was the place where she met
Luo Liang for the first time.

28:32.400 --> 28:33.330
Until her death,

28:33.640 --> 28:34.770
she still loved him.

28:40.680 --> 28:41.850
From He Xiao,

28:42.240 --> 28:42.880
to Xie Ke,

28:42.960 --> 28:44.220
and then to Wei Zhihua.

28:44.590 --> 28:46.550
For all three of them,
from meeting Luo Liang

28:46.550 --> 28:47.790
to their eventual suicides,

28:47.790 --> 28:49.960
the time intervals became shorter

28:49.960 --> 28:50.830
and shorter.

28:51.920 --> 28:54.790
Does this imply that he was getting
more and more skilled?

28:54.790 --> 28:56.640
Mister opened the Amusement Park Forum

28:56.640 --> 28:58.510
on the Internet in 2010

28:58.510 --> 29:00.350
and began posting those PUA Theories.

29:00.350 --> 29:01.920
In 2014,

29:02.440 --> 29:04.300
the Forum suddenly went offline.

29:04.400 --> 29:06.000
Mister disappeared as well.

29:06.270 --> 29:07.030
Why?

29:09.270 --> 29:11.200
Did he suddenly grow a conscience?

29:11.880 --> 29:12.680
Like a butcher dropped his knife

29:12.680 --> 29:14.140
and turned over a new leaf?

29:14.640 --> 29:16.770
Would a person like him drop his knife?

29:23.270 --> 29:25.670
I took a close look
at Xia Yi's screenshots.

29:26.350 --> 29:27.160
I think

29:28.400 --> 29:30.680
this Mister is different from Xia Yi

29:30.680 --> 29:32.430
or Ouyang.

29:33.480 --> 29:35.340
He's after neither money nor sex.

29:36.110 --> 29:38.880
He simply enjoys
the thrill of manipulation.

29:40.350 --> 29:41.550
According to his theory,

29:41.550 --> 29:44.270
he would drag other people into his logic

29:44.270 --> 29:46.930
and condescendingly attack
their weaknesses,

29:46.960 --> 29:48.550
forcing them to explain

29:47.880 --> 29:52.410
[July 15, 2019, Monday]

29:48.550 --> 29:49.880
and prove their love,

29:49.880 --> 29:52.030
until they feel guilty

29:52.030 --> 29:54.430
and think they are
never doing well enough.

29:55.160 --> 29:57.480
And once any prey
wants to escape this logic

29:57.480 --> 29:58.810
and have their own will,

29:58.920 --> 30:00.180
they will be punished.

30:01.440 --> 30:04.160
When they are on the verge of collapse,

30:03.820 --> 30:11.780
[July 15, 2019, Monday]

30:05.110 --> 30:07.910
Mister would suddenly become
incredibly gentle.

30:12.510 --> 30:13.940
It feels like...

30:14.550 --> 30:15.640
I suddenly choke you,

30:15.640 --> 30:17.370
and you're about to suffocate.

30:17.590 --> 30:18.850
Then I suddenly let go.

30:19.240 --> 30:21.440
This cycle repeats over and over again.

30:22.960 --> 30:23.970
The prey is

30:24.310 --> 30:25.800
like Pavlov's dog,

30:26.030 --> 30:28.570
eventually becoming completely docile.

30:29.110 --> 30:29.880
Well...

30:30.310 --> 30:31.550
If being with someone

30:31.550 --> 30:32.400
makes you suffer

30:32.400 --> 30:33.640
so much,

30:33.640 --> 30:35.000
why not just leave him?

30:36.960 --> 30:37.750
Do you remember

30:37.750 --> 30:40.070
the word "vacuum" in the screenshots?

30:41.110 --> 30:42.270
It means detaching the victim

30:42.270 --> 30:44.030
from all social relationships

30:44.030 --> 30:44.750
she has

30:45.070 --> 30:46.360
in order to isolate her

30:46.480 --> 30:48.880
and leave her
with only this man by her side.

30:50.640 --> 30:53.040
To put it simply, it's just brainwashing.

30:54.160 --> 30:55.560
That's not right either.

30:55.880 --> 30:57.160
Even if Luo Liang is

30:57.160 --> 30:58.160
really Mister...

30:59.440 --> 31:01.480
could Ms. Yan be brainwashed by him?

31:01.480 --> 31:02.350
Ms. Yan is

31:03.160 --> 31:04.550
so independent

31:04.550 --> 31:05.830
and clear-minded,

31:05.830 --> 31:08.310
and she is also quite fierce
when scolding people.

31:08.310 --> 31:10.750
She wouldn't be easily brainwashed.

31:13.790 --> 31:16.170
When did the last victim commit suicide?

31:16.550 --> 31:18.110
On March 15, 2013,

31:18.200 --> 31:19.600
Wei Zhihua hung herself.

31:20.310 --> 31:22.960
By 2014, when the Amusement Park
went offline,

31:22.960 --> 31:25.310
why had there been a gap of over a year?

31:32.470 --> 31:33.110
Yeah.

31:33.110 --> 31:34.790
Shouldn't serial offenders like this

31:34.790 --> 31:36.750
maintain a specific pattern?

31:39.510 --> 31:40.480
Unless...

31:40.480 --> 31:41.510
There was an accident.

31:41.510 --> 31:44.030
Right, if Mister didn't die,

31:44.110 --> 31:45.830
it's very likely
that there was an accident

31:45.830 --> 31:47.630
that made him feel threatened

31:48.200 --> 31:49.440
and suddenly shut down the website.

31:49.440 --> 31:51.000
In 2014, Luo Liang was

31:51.000 --> 31:53.640
interning at Edward Hospital
on Harbor Island.

31:53.640 --> 31:55.790
When he was in college,
getting his master's and PhD,

31:55.790 --> 31:57.000
there were victims all the time.

31:57.000 --> 31:58.680
So when he was working and interning,

31:58.680 --> 32:00.140
there should be some, too.

32:01.720 --> 32:04.050
Do you have a Harbor Island Travel Permit?

32:10.880 --> 32:11.960
Hello, Dr. Luo.

32:12.640 --> 32:13.680
Long time no see.

32:14.960 --> 32:16.490
How have you been recently?

32:18.070 --> 32:18.880
Not good.

32:19.680 --> 32:20.740
It's quite boring.

32:20.790 --> 32:22.050
There's no challenge.

32:22.640 --> 32:23.680
I've been thinking,

32:23.680 --> 32:25.160
if I could make
the abandoned Amusement Park

32:25.160 --> 32:26.790
reopen for business,

32:27.000 --> 32:29.860
only the thrill of riding a roller coaster
to the sky

32:30.030 --> 32:31.890
would be the ultimate happiness.

32:32.590 --> 32:33.440
What do you think?

32:33.440 --> 32:35.880
There are too many thrilling rides
in the Amusement Park,

32:35.880 --> 32:37.610
not suitable for you right now.

32:37.880 --> 32:38.830
My advice is

32:39.270 --> 32:41.030
that sometimes
you can do some charity work

32:41.030 --> 32:42.030
and help others.

32:42.360 --> 32:44.160
It will boost dopamine release.

32:46.350 --> 32:47.150
Charity work?

32:48.880 --> 32:50.140
Help me visit someone.

32:54.640 --> 32:55.350
Come on.

33:00.750 --> 33:01.960
Who are you?

33:05.750 --> 33:07.440
I'm your mother.

33:07.550 --> 33:08.270
Here.

33:09.680 --> 33:10.540
Did you forget?

33:10.640 --> 33:11.100
Come on.

33:11.400 --> 33:12.200
Eat some more.

33:12.790 --> 33:13.250
Come on.

33:15.310 --> 33:16.390
Bed 15 is

33:16.440 --> 33:17.750
scheduled for surgery this afternoon.

33:17.750 --> 33:19.640
Make sure to remind him
not to eat anything.

33:19.640 --> 33:20.440
Yes, Dr. Chen.

33:22.140 --> 33:23.800
How is that little girl doing?

33:24.640 --> 33:25.720
Everything is normal.

33:25.720 --> 33:27.640
That old lady is so good to Qiao Zishan.

33:27.640 --> 33:30.440
Even her biological mother might not
take care of her this carefully.

33:30.440 --> 33:32.790
It's a pity
that the girl's dementia is getting worse.

33:32.790 --> 33:33.680
She saw the old lady just now

33:33.680 --> 33:35.140
and even asked who she was.

33:35.790 --> 33:36.960
It's a good sign.

33:37.480 --> 33:39.280
It means she's slowly waking up.

33:39.430 --> 33:40.890
I'll go back to take a look.

33:52.070 --> 33:52.580
Hello?

33:52.750 --> 33:53.260
Ms. Yan,

33:53.480 --> 33:54.640
Mr. Ding is in critical condition

33:54.640 --> 33:56.440
and needs surgery immediately.

33:56.620 --> 34:00.040
[Patient Analysis]

33:57.400 --> 33:58.110
Glioma is

33:58.110 --> 34:00.180
a very serious brain disease.

34:01.680 --> 34:03.010
If not controlled well,

34:03.030 --> 34:04.460
it will develop very rapidly.

34:04.460 --> 34:07.170
[Patient Analysis]

34:05.750 --> 34:07.350
The tumor has deteriorated,

34:07.480 --> 34:08.810
pressing on the nerves.

34:09.550 --> 34:10.949
If not handled in time...

34:11.880 --> 34:13.739
This surgery is extremely risky.

34:13.980 --> 34:15.280
But without the surgery,

34:15.280 --> 34:17.610
Mr. Ding probably won't survive tonight.

34:18.070 --> 34:20.440
Mr. Ding has authorized you
to manage his treatment.

34:20.440 --> 34:22.040
This is the surgical consent form.

34:21.710 --> 34:24.679
[Patient, Agent, Signature]

34:22.480 --> 34:23.540
You need to sign it.

34:24.500 --> 34:25.699
Without the surgery,

34:25.880 --> 34:28.210
Mr. Ding probably won't survive tonight.

34:28.480 --> 34:29.610
You need to sign it.

34:39.489 --> 34:40.110
Ms. Yan,

34:40.400 --> 34:41.730
have some coffee first.

34:43.670 --> 34:45.550
I've already signed everything I need to.

34:45.550 --> 34:46.360
It's getting late.

34:46.360 --> 34:47.320
I've got to go.

34:47.320 --> 34:48.320
You can't, Ms. Yan.

34:48.320 --> 34:49.630
The doctor specifically instructed

34:49.630 --> 34:51.230
that if there are any complications
during the surgery,

34:51.230 --> 34:52.889
we need your signature again.

34:55.980 --> 34:57.330
Why did he come back?

34:57.960 --> 34:59.360
Wasn't he abroad?

35:02.230 --> 35:04.510
He wanted to come back
for some interviews.

35:04.510 --> 35:06.150
Many media outlets wanted to talk to him

35:06.150 --> 35:07.350
about those letters.

35:08.110 --> 35:11.370
He said he wanted to clear his name
as well as the company's.

35:17.180 --> 35:22.100
[July 16, 2019, Tuesday]

35:29.130 --> 35:33.840
[July 16, 2019, Tuesday]

35:36.320 --> 35:41.510
[July 16, 2019, Tuesday]

35:53.580 --> 35:56.340
[Honey]

36:07.880 --> 36:08.400
Hello?

36:09.360 --> 36:10.160
Hello, Honey.

36:11.230 --> 36:12.590
I'm almost home.

36:12.840 --> 36:14.370
What's for dinner tonight?

36:16.590 --> 36:17.760
I'm not home.

36:18.280 --> 36:19.280
I'm out right now.

36:20.670 --> 36:21.400
Really?

36:22.880 --> 36:23.810
Where did you go?

36:24.170 --> 36:25.430
Why didn't you tell me?

36:26.110 --> 36:27.840
Would you like me to pick you up?

36:29.550 --> 36:30.570
The surgery was successful.

36:30.570 --> 36:31.740
Mr. Ding survived.

36:33.070 --> 36:33.750
Don't worry,

36:33.750 --> 36:34.400
Ms. Yan.

37:25.880 --> 37:26.400
Why?

37:31.800 --> 37:33.070
Why did you go save him?

37:33.760 --> 37:35.810
If I hadn't happened to call you,

37:36.400 --> 37:38.800
you wouldn't be going
to tell me, would you?

37:40.230 --> 37:40.960
I'm sorry.

37:42.920 --> 37:43.800
I kept thinking

37:43.800 --> 37:46.060
about how to bring this up,

37:46.880 --> 37:50.080
or maybe it'd be better
not to say anything about it at all.

37:50.550 --> 37:52.350
I really didn't want his affairs

37:52.590 --> 37:54.550
to disturb you or hurt you again.

37:55.400 --> 37:56.110
Hurt me?

37:58.590 --> 37:59.740
So you were worried

38:00.110 --> 38:02.170
that me finding out you still love him

38:02.440 --> 38:03.440
would hurt me?

38:03.880 --> 38:05.540
It's not like that, of course.

38:06.630 --> 38:08.630
I didn't save him because I love him.

38:08.630 --> 38:09.570
Then why?

38:17.000 --> 38:17.840
If he dies,

38:17.840 --> 38:18.920
that's his fate.

38:19.840 --> 38:21.190
But if I refused to sign

38:21.190 --> 38:22.660
and caused him to die,

38:23.190 --> 38:24.070
if I did that,

38:24.440 --> 38:26.240
I would be no different from him.

38:26.840 --> 38:27.900
Losing my humanity

38:28.150 --> 38:29.410
just to get back at him,

38:30.880 --> 38:32.010
I really can't do it.

38:35.150 --> 38:36.750
You really are a good person.

38:45.760 --> 38:46.480
A good girl

38:48.190 --> 38:51.190
who didn't fight back
even when he stripped you naked,

38:51.800 --> 38:53.530
and just swallowed your pride.

38:54.480 --> 38:57.010
That's why he chose you
since you were little,

38:57.280 --> 38:58.480
made you fall for him,

39:00.190 --> 39:02.050
and did whatever he wanted to you.

39:03.480 --> 39:04.190
And then,

39:04.670 --> 39:07.230
he could still harass you
over a decade later

39:08.230 --> 39:10.710
and use his life
to test your love for him.

39:11.440 --> 39:12.360
I don't love him.

39:12.360 --> 39:13.170
You know that.

39:14.670 --> 39:16.320
It's all his fault. You said it.

39:16.320 --> 39:17.710
It's all his fault.

39:18.630 --> 39:19.360
Why?

39:21.190 --> 39:22.150
Tell me why.

39:23.070 --> 39:25.170
How could he do this?

39:25.440 --> 39:27.480
Why did you allow him to do this?

39:27.550 --> 39:29.320
No. No.

39:29.840 --> 39:32.070
I've done my best to support you,

39:32.630 --> 39:33.550
but have you ever considered

39:33.550 --> 39:35.030
my feelings at all?

39:36.400 --> 39:37.280
Tell me.

39:37.880 --> 39:38.840
Did you

39:38.880 --> 39:41.480
write those letters yourself,
word for word?

39:42.630 --> 39:43.360
No.

39:44.550 --> 39:44.960
No.

39:44.960 --> 39:46.230
"I miss you."

39:49.360 --> 39:50.360
"Every night,

39:50.670 --> 39:52.900
I dream of growing up faster

39:53.630 --> 39:55.300
to become a real woman,

39:56.030 --> 39:56.960
your woman."

39:58.630 --> 39:59.460
Stop. Stop.

40:02.960 --> 40:04.600
You wrote them.

40:04.880 --> 40:06.150
You said in your letters,

40:06.150 --> 40:08.420
"This is how we love each other.

40:08.840 --> 40:10.150
It's the ultimate thing

40:10.150 --> 40:12.360
two people in love can do.

40:13.480 --> 40:14.230
I belong to you,

40:14.230 --> 40:15.430
and you belong to me."

40:16.320 --> 40:17.480
You said in your letters

40:17.480 --> 40:19.280
that your love transcended age,

40:19.590 --> 40:21.320
and you got over all taboos

40:21.920 --> 40:23.320
to express this love.

40:23.630 --> 40:25.760
You asked him
why he distanced himself from you.

40:25.760 --> 40:27.530
You said that you were missing him

40:27.530 --> 40:28.630
-I don't love him.
-every night.

40:28.630 --> 40:29.440
It's not true.

40:29.440 --> 40:31.630
-You wanted him to hug you.
-I don't love him.

40:31.630 --> 40:33.520
It's not true. Stop reciting.

40:33.550 --> 40:36.550
-I don't want to remember it either!
-I'm begging you.

40:37.000 --> 40:38.890
But every word you wrote is

40:39.190 --> 40:41.560
deeply engraved in my mind.

40:42.280 --> 40:44.940
No matter how professional
a psychiatrist I am,

40:45.630 --> 40:47.030
or how accepting I can be,

40:47.480 --> 40:49.710
I am still a normal man.

40:51.880 --> 40:54.420
You used words of love
you've never said to me

40:54.630 --> 40:57.030
to confess your love so passionately
to another man.

40:57.030 --> 40:58.130
I don't love him.

40:58.360 --> 40:59.360
It's not like that.

40:59.360 --> 41:01.360
How can you expect me to accept this?

41:02.480 --> 41:04.340
How can you expect me not to be sad?

41:09.230 --> 41:10.350
You said

41:12.000 --> 41:14.480
you can't forgive yourself

41:16.550 --> 41:17.690
because

41:18.440 --> 41:20.240
you had happy moments together.

41:25.400 --> 41:26.260
Happy moments.

41:26.960 --> 41:27.670
No.

41:30.510 --> 41:32.050
What kind of happiness was it?

41:32.050 --> 41:32.880
No.

41:33.480 --> 41:35.960
Was it the happiness
of giving your first time to him?

41:35.960 --> 41:36.840
Don't say it.

41:40.360 --> 41:41.110
Stop it.

41:41.110 --> 41:42.920
It's not true. I didn't!

41:43.150 --> 41:44.880
You gave your first time to him.

41:44.880 --> 41:45.840
The happiness of you

41:45.840 --> 41:47.840
belonging to him,
and him belonging to you.

41:47.840 --> 41:48.510
No.

41:48.880 --> 41:49.590
Was it?

41:50.030 --> 41:50.630
Right?

41:52.840 --> 41:53.400
Did it

41:53.400 --> 41:54.360
make you

41:54.360 --> 41:55.890
happier than being with me?

41:57.150 --> 41:58.220
To love you,

41:58.440 --> 41:59.900
I've endured everything.

41:59.920 --> 42:02.380
I've endured
your disgusting past with him.

42:04.080 --> 42:05.490
And how did you treat me?

42:06.630 --> 42:08.890
With agony you can't imagine, I accepted

42:09.480 --> 42:11.990
that you loved a man like him.

42:12.320 --> 42:13.440
I don't love him.

42:15.030 --> 42:16.300
I don't love him.

42:17.360 --> 42:18.350
It's not true.

42:19.150 --> 42:20.110
How did you repay me?

42:20.110 --> 42:21.400
Stop talking.

42:23.280 --> 42:24.340
You still love him.

42:24.510 --> 42:25.110
No.

42:26.320 --> 42:27.780
You still went to save him.

42:29.480 --> 42:29.880
No.

42:30.320 --> 42:30.930
Honey,

42:30.960 --> 42:31.930
I only love you.

42:31.960 --> 42:32.710
I don't love him.

42:32.710 --> 42:33.900
I really don't love him.

42:33.900 --> 42:34.920
I only love you.

42:35.030 --> 42:36.030
I only love you!

42:36.030 --> 42:37.380
Please, forgive me.

42:37.480 --> 42:39.670
I'm so sorry. I'm so sorry.

42:39.670 --> 42:40.440
Let go of me!

42:43.670 --> 42:44.280
Honey.

42:58.800 --> 42:59.590
Open the door,

42:59.590 --> 43:00.410
Honey.

43:00.480 --> 43:02.120
Please open the door.

43:02.320 --> 43:03.320
I only love you.

43:03.320 --> 43:04.340
I don't love him.

43:05.030 --> 43:06.080
I beg you.

43:06.670 --> 43:07.400
I really

43:07.510 --> 43:08.890
only love you.

43:08.960 --> 43:10.170
I don't love him.

43:10.630 --> 43:11.850
I don't love him.

43:11.960 --> 43:13.820
I really don't love him.

43:16.510 --> 43:17.730
I don't love him.

43:17.840 --> 43:19.280
I really don't love him.

43:44.120 --> 43:48.460
[The Dark Romance]

43:58.280 --> 43:59.030
Cola?

44:00.320 --> 44:01.160
Cola,

44:01.550 --> 44:02.350
is that you?

44:02.550 --> 44:03.280
Cola.

44:05.800 --> 44:06.550
Cola.

44:18.110 --> 44:18.590
Mom?

44:23.920 --> 44:25.760
You got them killed.

44:28.150 --> 44:30.230
It was you who got them killed.
